    "Since the ratio of 1star rated reviews to 5-star reviews is low, the dataset is unbalanced so the model is in favor of predicting positive reviews easier.",
    "As far as the classification of fake and truthful reviews, there is no hard evidence that all short reviews are fake.",
    "Similarly, it is possible that longer reviews contain fake reviews.",
